"Peppa the pig," yes.
Scott Coker, the president of Bellator, said they would be working on their programming to include British viewers in the future.
“I think when I think about rebroadcasting, I think we can probably find a solution,” Coker said.
“However, it’s six o’clock in the morning on a Sunday and we won’t be able to find a solution until Sunday our time, or Monday their time.
